---
import ChartJsBlock from '../../../components/ChartJsBlock.astro';
import SparklineChart from '../../../components/SparklineChart.astro';
import SimpleBarChart from '../../../components/SimpleBarChart.astro';
---

  <section class="component-group" id="group-charts">
    <header class="component-group__header">
      <h2>Charts</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Chart.js</strong> cho biểu đồ chuẩn (bar, line, doughnut, radar, polar). Phía dưới giữ
        <code>SimpleBarChart</code> / <code>SparklineChart</code> khi cần SVG nhẹ, không bundle thư viện.
      </p>
    </header>

  {/* ─────── Chart.js ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="chartjs">
    <h3>Chart.js</h3>
    <p>
      Dependency: <code>chart.js</code>. Component <code>ChartJsBlock.astro</code> khởi tạo canvas trong
      <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> (bundle Vite), màu trục đọc từ CSS variables.
    </p>
    <div class="example-render example-render--charts">
      <ChartJsBlock
        id="kit-chart-bar"
        type="bar"
        title="Bar — latency theo tool (demo)"
        height={220}
        labels={['bash', 'read', 'edit', 'grep', 'agent']}
        datasets={[
          { label: 'p50 (ms)', data: [38, 95, 210, 120, 640] },
          { label: 'p99 (ms)', data: [120, 280, 890, 400, 2400] },
        ]}
      />
      <ChartJsBlock
        id="kit-chart-line"
        type="line"
        title="Line — token / step (tĩnh)"
        height={200}
        labels={['1', '2', '3', '4', '5', '6', '7', '8']}
        datasets={[{ label: 'tokens', data: [120, 340, 290, 510, 480, 620, 590, 710] }]}
      />
      <div class="chart-js-row">
        <ChartJsBlock
          id="kit-chart-doughnut"
          type="doughnut"
          title="Doughnut — thời gian theo phase"
          height={240}
          labels={['LLM', 'tools', 'IO', 'idle']}
          datasets={[{ label: 'share', data: [52, 28, 12, 8] }]}
        />
        <ChartJsBlock
          id="kit-chart-radar"
          type="radar"
          title="Radar — so khía cạnh (1–10)"
          height={260}
          labels={['Speed', 'Safety', 'DX', 'Cost', 'Observability']}
          datasets={[
            { label: 'A', data: [8, 6, 9, 5, 7] },
            { label: 'B', data: [6, 9, 7, 8, 6] },
          ]}
        />
      </div>
      <ChartJsBlock
        id="kit-chart-polar"
        type="polarArea"
        title="Polar area — workload (tuỳ chọn)"
        height={240}
        labels={['ingest', 'plan', 'act', 'verify', 'report']}
        datasets={[{ label: 'weight', data: [11, 16, 22, 9, 14] }]}
      />
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`import ChartJsBlock from '../../components/ChartJsBlock.astro';

<ChartJsBlock
  id="my-bar"
  type="bar"
  labels={['A', 'B']}
  datasets={[{ label: 'ms', data: [10, 20] }]}
/>`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── SimpleBarChart ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="simplebarchart">
    <h3>SimpleBarChart</h3>
    <p>Thanh ngang theo nhãn + giá trị; scale theo max trong data hoặc prop <code>max</code>.</p>
    <div class="example-render">
      <SimpleBarChart
        title="Tool latency (demo)"
        unit="ms"
        items={[
          { label: 'bash', value: 42, variant: 'green' },
          { label: 'read', value: 120, variant: 'cyan' },
          { label: 'edit', value: 280, variant: 'amber' },
          { label: 'agent loop', value: 890, variant: 'purple' },
        ]}
      />
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<SimpleBarChart
  title="Latency"
  unit="ms"
  items={[
    { label: 'bash', value: 42, variant: 'green' },
    { label: 'edit', value: 280, variant: 'amber' },
  ]}
/>`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── SparklineChart ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="sparklinechart">
    <h3>SparklineChart</h3>
    <p>Đường trend tối giản — ít nhất 2 điểm số. Màu theo <code>--accent</code>.</p>
    <div class="example-render">
      <SparklineChart
        values={[12, 18, 14, 22, 19, 28, 24, 31]}
        caption="Token / step (ví dụ)"
        width={240}
        height={40}
      />
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<SparklineChart
  values={[12, 18, 14, 22]}
  caption="Trend label"
  width={200}
  height={36}
/>`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  </section>
